{
  "stem": "24515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "On November the 10th, 9th, the Kristallnacht--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know, his lawyer and his--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember that he was perfectly straightforwardly elected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tend to forget that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That he had a proper majority.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, I know that I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, this was-- this was-- it was not good for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "More seriously, that this was not something that we would have wished.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as I told you before, I was 11 at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our parents went out of their way to try to protect us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that I don't know that this made a very major-- had a very major influence on my life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Except on little things like, you know, my mother, very soon after he was in power, they took-- got out the Nuremberg laws and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember my mother very sharply saying to my brother and me, to whatever we did, never to look at, never mind talk to or touch, a German Aryan girl.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, then a little bit later, you see, '34, '35-- so it went step by step.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Jews were prohibited to go to the parks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were prohibited to go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure what the sequence of this was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One after the other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, long before Kristallnacht, we are not permitted to go to museums or theaters and so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my mother taking me to the German-- to the Chemnitz theater-- which was quite a respectable theater-- when a famous German actress by the name of Kathe Dorsch-- I remember her-- was there to play Schiller, a game-- a play by Schiller.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother took us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
